title: Louis Vuitton Kensington Tote Bag
description: Louis Vuitton Kensington tote in Damier coated canvas (year 2016). Featuring gold-toned hardware, dual top handles, exterior 'V' signature & snap buttons on sides. The top opens to a beige microfiber interior with two compartments divided by a central zip pocket. Approx dimensions: 34cm(Base-L) x 26cm(H) x 15cm(D), handle drop 12cm and 39cm detachable shoulder strap drop. Accompanied by Louis Vuitton dustbag and shopping bag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
